{"tid":803471,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟娶處女做老婆有幾重要? 結婚個日你咪知囉","createTime":"2018-09-02T09:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T15:05:17.000Z","uid":78016,"like":10,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fb351505706791eb300a7c0c42b41d6e04b42dd5","tid":803471,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:53:48.000Z","msg":"我唔直接答你 我用例子答你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係黑鮑老公面前希哥一定微笑到最後<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2018/05/31/010090672.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fnews%2Fsystem%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F010090672.shtml&d=ZlKfbH7KqDG2KqnAb5yh1nIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6cd5e2e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2018/05/31/010090672.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;你老婆好好砌喎&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n&quot;你老婆 好黑喎&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你係黑鮑老公 即使你同黑鮑結左婚 你永遠都係希哥 甚至全世界面前抬唔起頭<br />\n無錯 你老婆有床上技術或pose 服待你 俾你影 但一諗起佢的過去 點俾人影相 點滿足希哥嘅淫慾<br />\n你只能每日以淚洗面<br />\n心裏面諗 技術我都可以教佢 點解要其他人教 點解佢個處唔係我破<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反如果你娶左個處女做老婆 就唔會有呢d 煩惱<br />\n<br />\n註: 處女老婆可以指為結婚時係處女 或者只有新郎一人進入過佢個西"},{"pid":"5088cd2a56ac1328c7bccdac72c0f66709c9f8d2","tid":803471,"uid":132587,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:55:31.000Z","msg":"今日最後一個暑假 好好珍惜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca39a5519d56aa6253b9f07b0d12c6219257e423","tid":803471,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:56:32.000Z","msg":"答返佢地囉，唔緊要，入左5cm後就新的一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cda51a2df3620831ab1dfce961e92c0f6c9a89","tid":803471,"uid":194609,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:58:24.000Z","msg":"老母係處緊要d"},{"pid":"f